:"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33772,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/13\/umar-scholars-gatherings\/","url_meta":{"origin":11242,"position":2},"title":"Umar on &#8216;Ilm: No gathering more noble than a scholar&#8217;s class","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Ghazali reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, a man might leave his house with sins like the mountain of Tihamah, but then he hears some knowledge and fear Allah, forsakes his sins and departs to his house without any sin upon him. Do not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15344,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/dua-expiation-sins-assembly\/","url_meta":{"origin":11242,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication to expiate sins in gathering","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Barzah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say some final words when intending to leave an assembly, \u201cO Allah, glory and praise be to You. I testify there is no God but You, I ask Your forgiveness, and I repent to You.\u201d A\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img"